It is officially my birthday month!! 🎂 🥳 I will now begin dropping “subtle” hints to Momma 🐻 about  all of the many things that I “need!” 🎁 😛 
——————————————————————————
Happy January to everypawdy! Momma 🐻 here! On a serious note (and perhaps contrary to what he may believe, lol), Bacon does not “need” anything for his birthday! We are actually working with his school @whatdogswant to throw him possibly the most epic CorgVegas themed corgi birthday party that the world has ever known! We are so excited to host many of his friends from near and far to celebrate our “not so little” boy turning the BIG 3! We have received many DMs and inquiries about possibly sending Bacon presents for his birthday. We are truly overwhelmed and so grateful for all of the love that Bacon receives! As such, much like his 😇 big brother (Colton 🐻) made a practice of doing, we would like to try to spread the love around this year for his birthday. We are excited to encourage anyone that is wanting to send Bacon something for his birthday to please consider making a donation to Paws and Effect Medical and Maternal Rescue (located in Mesa, AZ)! We will share the donation link in our bio for anyone interested in participating! Please send us a DM if you make a donation so that we can send you one of Bacon’s pawesome birthday stickers! 
PS: Bacon was able to get a @snoozerpets bed (pictured in the reel) and he is obsessed with it! #spoileddog
Know what’s on the menu? Me ‘n’ u. 😂 💋 #cheesypickuplines #dapperdog #bananarepublic

Happy freaking birthday to me!!! 🥳 I had the best day EVER on Saturday at my CorgVegas themed 3rd birthday party at What Dogs Want Academy! 🎲🥂🎰 
We have sooooo many people to thank for helping to make CorgVegas come to life! To begin, thank you to @rock_house_frenchies for all of the absolutely amazing casino/vegas themed desserts, food, and decorations (and the countless hours of love and preparation that went into everything that you do!) You’re the best! Thank you to Stefanie and the best dog school in the world @whatdogswant ❤️ We love you and all of your amazing team! Thank you to Olia and @mishka_dog_cakes for creating the most gorgeous and yummy CorgVegas themed cake that the world has ever known! Thank you to our pawesome DJs @niceneasymusic and our amazing marquee letter peeps @desertglowco ❤️ Thank you to @cliveandbacon for the adorable custom bandanas for me and my guests. Thank you to @goodboydogbeer for the yummy dog beer for me and all of my corgi besties and to @woofboard for making the cutest and tastiest CorgVegas barkuterie boards and for donating to our prizes! Thank you to our faves at @pridegroomnyc for the pawesome samples for our goodie bags! Thank you to @crumpsnaturals for donating delicious treats for my 4 legged guests as well! Thank you to @sewdoggonecreative and @jaymatkk for helping with my costumes and momma bear’s CorgVegas shirt! Thank you to @evolutionized_photography for taking some great pics! Lastly, (but certainly not least), thank you to all of our amazing friends/guests that came from near and FAR (and those that were there in spirit and via IG) to celebrate with us! We appreciate all of the love and donations that were generously made to @pawsandeffect.medicalrescue ❤️‍🩹 Vanessa (Paws and Effect) is truly a special person and we applaud her heroic efforts to help pups each and every day. Momma 🐻 has said it before and will continue to say that the corgi community is truly a magical group! We are so thankful for all of you!! #CorgVegas #HappyBirthdayBacon #VivaCorgVegas #3rdBirthday #ItsMyDogsBirthday 🥳🎰🥂🎲🍾🃏🍺 🥳

social_posts.post_text:
Life motto: More good times! 🏜️ 🎉 
Please enjoy a quick recap of our trip to Sedona last weekend after my amazing CorgVegas 3rd Birthday pawty! This trip was the perfect finale to a truly epic long birthday weekend! We were hosted by our friends at @hiltonsedona for this adventure; and they definitely did not disappoint! Hilton Sedona recently relaunched their Pet Pals Package with enhanced offerings! You can check it out here: 
https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/sdxsehh-hilton-sedona-resort-at-bell-rock/offers/
Sisfur @corgiclubaspen and I enjoyed all of the items off of the pet menu (breakfast and lunch/dinner options); a fun bark box, tons of fun photo opportunities; and a beautiful dinner with momma 🐻 and corgdad in one of the lighted igloos! I can see why my 😇 big brother, Colton, loved @hiltonsedona soooo much! We truly can’t wait to go back!! 10/10 recommend!!

Are you a judge? 
Because I’m feeling the need to court you right now 🥰😘😍

3/20 is always a rough day for us; as it is the day that my 😇 big brother, Colton 🐻, went to heaven. We know that he is with us every day (he is momma’s soulmate), but it is always a tough day to get through. Hi IG Friends and Family! Momma 🐻 here: We hope that everyone is having a good week.
